20
00:01:40,240 --> 00:01:42,960
The Prince of Tennis
~ Match! Tennis Juniors! ~

21
00:01:49,680 --> 00:01:52,520
See you. We'll go to watch your game.

22
00:01:52,600 --> 00:01:53,600
-Mm-hm.
-[chuckling]

23
00:01:53,680 --> 00:01:55,000
-Bye.
-Bye.

24
00:01:56,880 --> 00:01:57,720
[Coach Muyun mutters]

25
00:01:58,400 --> 00:01:59,360
Let's go.

26
00:02:00,880 --> 00:02:02,640
-Did you have fun?
-Yes.

27
00:02:03,720 --> 00:02:06,520
Eh? Let me see your racket.

28
00:02:07,240 --> 00:02:08,880
Hey, sit.

29
00:02:10,479 --> 00:02:11,600
Hmm.

30
00:02:14,880 --> 00:02:15,720
Oh.

31
00:02:16,080 --> 00:02:17,240
The strings hold up well.

32
00:02:19,080 --> 00:02:20,480
[sighs, clicks tongue]

33
00:02:20,920 --> 00:02:22,600
This grip tape won't do.

34
00:02:24,200 --> 00:02:25,720
-[gasps]
-Oh.

35
00:02:26,520 --> 00:02:27,680
What are you worrying about?

36
00:02:27,760 --> 00:02:28,880
You don't trust me?

37
00:02:29,080 --> 00:02:31,080
[chuckling]
Hey.

38
00:02:31,720 --> 00:02:34,240
Let me tell you a little secret.

39
00:02:34,480 --> 00:02:36,640
[Coach Muyun] I fell in love with a girl

40
00:02:37,280 --> 00:02:38,880
when I was your age.

41
00:02:40,440 --> 00:02:41,760
In order to court her,

42
00:02:42,920 --> 00:02:45,040
I wrote romantic poems every day.

43
00:02:45,120 --> 00:02:46,480
Did you get her then?

44
00:02:46,560 --> 00:02:47,440
[groans]

45
00:02:47,520 --> 00:02:49,040
I was a terrible poet.

46
00:02:49,800 --> 00:02:51,160
The girl ran away.

47
00:02:51,440 --> 00:02:56,760
But I've loved writing poetry
ever since then.

48
00:02:57,640 --> 00:02:58,720
Then what?

49
00:02:59,160 --> 00:03:02,320
Hard work always pays off.

50
00:03:02,960 --> 00:03:04,640
Finally, I had a poem

51
00:03:05,200 --> 00:03:07,160
published in the newspaper.
[chuckles]

52
00:03:07,240 --> 00:03:09,080
I don't think that's a great success.

53
00:03:09,440 --> 00:03:10,320
Hey.

54
00:03:10,760 --> 00:03:13,360
If you only think about how to succeed
whenever you do anything,

55
00:03:13,800 --> 00:03:14,880
it won't do you any good.

56
00:03:15,320 --> 00:03:19,240
You'd better think about
the significance of what you're doing

57
00:03:19,880 --> 00:03:21,080
right now.

58
00:03:21,640 --> 00:03:23,640
[light music]

59
00:03:24,680 --> 00:03:26,280
I want to improve myself.

60
00:03:27,840 --> 00:03:28,840
Why?

61
00:03:29,800 --> 00:03:31,920
Because I want
to beat everyone in front of me.

62
00:03:32,440 --> 00:03:33,600
Aren't you tired?

63
00:03:33,680 --> 00:03:34,520
No.

64
00:03:34,600 --> 00:03:36,880
[soft chuckle]
Boy, you are still young.

65
00:03:38,160 --> 00:03:40,120
And you do love playing tennis.

66
00:03:40,320 --> 00:03:41,600
I don't only love playing tennis.

67
00:03:41,840 --> 00:03:43,000
I love winning even more.

68
00:03:44,040 --> 00:03:46,560
Even though we all play to win,

69
00:03:47,040 --> 00:03:49,280
we should try to savor the joy

70
00:03:49,360 --> 00:03:53,200
that every tennis game gives us.

71
00:03:53,920 --> 00:03:56,520
[Coach Muyun]
Playing tennis is like traveling.

72
00:03:56,600 --> 00:03:59,960
The journey is more important
than the destination.

73
00:04:00,840 --> 00:04:02,880
Uh, look at my boys.

74
00:04:02,960 --> 00:04:06,760
They are happy
as long as they can play tennis.

75
00:04:07,600 --> 00:04:10,720
Don't you ever have such feelings?

76
00:04:12,960 --> 00:04:13,880
[snickers]

77
00:04:14,200 --> 00:04:16,600
Don't worry. You have plenty of time.

78
00:04:16,680 --> 00:04:17,560
Take it easy.

79
00:04:18,160 --> 00:04:20,680
But remember.

80
00:04:21,440 --> 00:04:24,920
Don't ignore the happiness
on your journey.

81
00:04:25,240 --> 00:04:26,240
[Coach Muyun] Hm?

82
00:04:26,480 --> 00:04:27,760
[chuckles]
It's done.

83
00:04:28,960 --> 00:04:29,880
[Coach Muyun groans]

84
00:04:30,360 --> 00:04:31,480
Here.

85
00:04:33,080 --> 00:04:35,160
I hope you play well in your game.

86
00:04:35,960 --> 00:04:36,840
Bye.

87
00:04:39,160 --> 00:04:40,200
[sighs]

88
00:04:41,080 --> 00:04:43,160
What is your last poem about?

89
00:04:45,520 --> 00:04:47,240
"Poem"? Oh...

90
00:04:47,600 --> 00:04:49,200
[Coach Muyun] Let me read it for you.

91
00:04:50,000 --> 00:04:52,320
"Glory is as superficial as a dream.

92
00:04:52,400 --> 00:04:54,760
Awards are merely some notes
written in your biography.

93
00:04:55,120 --> 00:04:57,480
One's career can be a place
as dangerous as the deep sea.

94
00:04:57,560 --> 00:04:59,240
What's the point in getting up early

95
00:04:59,320 --> 00:05:01,360
in a freezing winter
to practice just to beat others?"

96
00:05:01,840 --> 00:05:02,960
[Coach Muyun laughs]

97
00:05:04,800 --> 00:05:07,680
XING YAO

98
00:05:08,040 --> 00:05:13,320
18 DAYS BEFORE YU QING VS XING YAO

99
00:05:13,400 --> 00:05:15,400
[upbeat music]

100
00:05:17,240 --> 00:05:18,640
So this is Xing Yao.

101
00:05:25,000 --> 00:05:25,960
[camera shutter clicks]

102
00:05:40,200 --> 00:05:42,640
Hello, I am the coach
of the Xing Yao tennis club.

103
00:05:42,720 --> 00:05:43,760
My last name is Fu.

104
00:05:44,040 --> 00:05:46,080
I am a reporter from Tennis Monthly.

105
00:05:46,160 --> 00:05:48,120
-You can call me Sha.
-Okay.

106
00:05:48,200 --> 00:05:50,800
Your team seems to be pretty relaxed.

107
00:05:50,880 --> 00:05:51,760
That's true.

108
00:05:52,040 --> 00:05:54,160
We've almost finished
the school qualifying.

109
00:05:54,480 --> 00:05:57,760
You can interview the qualified players
and take photos of them.

110
00:05:58,360 --> 00:05:59,640
I've arranged everything for you.

111
00:06:01,320 --> 00:06:02,280
Hmm.

112
00:06:03,040 --> 00:06:04,200
Thanks.

113
00:06:05,920 --> 00:06:07,320
FENG ZHIYUAN

114
00:06:07,960 --> 00:06:09,280
Feng Zhiyuan.

115
00:06:11,080 --> 00:06:13,080
[tense music]

116
00:06:14,240 --> 00:06:15,240
[Sha] Feng Zhiyuan

117
00:06:15,320 --> 00:06:17,400
is famous for his ultra-fast,
mighty serve.

118
00:06:18,160 --> 00:06:19,240
-[grunts]
-[thwacks]

119
00:06:22,040 --> 00:06:23,400
[Sha] Yue Yang.

120
00:06:23,800 --> 00:06:24,840
[gasps]

121
00:06:24,920 --> 00:06:27,960
[Sha] Yue Yang has good flexibility
and a quick response.

122
00:06:28,040 --> 00:06:29,680
He's good at freestyle shots.

123
00:06:32,000 --> 00:06:33,120
YUE YANG
XING YAO HIGH SCHOOL PLAYER

124
00:06:35,720 --> 00:06:36,560
HUA CHONGHONG

125
00:06:36,640 --> 00:06:38,280
Hua Chonghong.

126
00:06:38,360 --> 00:06:42,040
[Sha] Hua Chonghong
has superhuman strength and a pure heart.

127
00:06:42,120 --> 00:06:44,280
He is an all-rounder
with both skill and strength.

128
00:06:45,360 --> 00:06:46,480
HUA CHONGHONG
XING YAO HIGH SCHOOL PLAYER

129
00:06:46,560 --> 00:06:48,080
[Sha] You Shixing.

130
00:06:48,680 --> 00:06:50,880
You Shixing is a mysterious talent

131
00:06:50,960 --> 00:06:52,360
and a perfect net player.

132
00:06:52,440 --> 00:06:54,960
He is a talented player
with thousands of tricks.

133
00:06:55,160 --> 00:06:56,720
Yue Yang and You Shixing's doubles team

134
00:06:56,800 --> 00:06:58,640
didn't lost a single game last year.

135
00:07:00,080 --> 00:07:01,920
JI JINGWU

136
00:07:02,480 --> 00:07:04,320
Ji Jingwu.

137
00:07:06,120 --> 00:07:07,280
[thwacks]

138
00:07:13,280 --> 00:07:16,120
[Sha] Ji Jingwu
is a talented all-round player.

139
00:07:16,200 --> 00:07:17,640
He is the soul of the tennis club.

140
00:07:21,920 --> 00:07:23,040
[camera shutter clicks]

141
00:07:29,480 --> 00:07:30,480
[snaps]

142
00:07:33,320 --> 00:07:34,400
[camera shutter clicking]

143
00:07:44,200 --> 00:07:46,120
Use these retouched photos
for your report.

144
00:07:48,080 --> 00:07:49,160
[gasps]

145
00:07:50,800 --> 00:07:52,800
[comical music]

146
00:07:53,760 --> 00:07:55,040
[sighs sharply]

147
00:08:05,640 --> 00:08:07,000
[Sha] Hu Liangliang.

148
00:08:07,920 --> 00:08:08,840
Hu Liangliang.

149
00:08:08,920 --> 00:08:11,480
A right-handed
defense and counter-attack player.

150
00:08:12,040 --> 00:08:14,400
His unique skill
is the ultrafast super volley

151
00:08:14,480 --> 00:08:15,960
and the Blockade Australian formation.

152
00:08:16,160 --> 00:08:17,800
[umpire 1] 6-0. Hu Liangliang won.

153
00:08:20,920 --> 00:08:22,280
HU LIANGLIANG
XING YAO HIGH SCHOOL PLAYER

154
00:08:22,960 --> 00:08:23,800
Yes!

155
00:08:24,920 --> 00:08:28,520
[Sha] Is he the one who lost to Xu Ziping?

156
00:08:32,000 --> 00:08:33,039
[camera shutter clicks]

157
00:08:37,200 --> 00:08:38,760
The last member of our main force...

158
00:08:40,760 --> 00:08:42,280
goes to our bench player,

159
00:08:43,039 --> 00:08:44,039
Ji Nuo.

160
00:08:45,159 --> 00:08:46,120
[gasps]

161
00:08:46,400 --> 00:08:48,960
Let's take a rest and get ready
for the next training session.

162
00:08:49,320 --> 00:08:50,320
Coach.

163
00:08:50,760 --> 00:08:51,760
[Liangliang gasps]

164
00:08:52,040 --> 00:08:53,360
Don't make a fool of yourself.

165
00:08:54,360 --> 00:08:56,880
[panting]
Captain.

166
00:08:59,640 --> 00:09:00,800
JI NUO
XING YAO HIGH SCHOOL PLAYER

167
00:09:00,880 --> 00:09:01,880
[Liangliang] I won.

168
00:09:02,520 --> 00:09:04,520
[ominous music]

169
00:09:05,120 --> 00:09:07,440
But it also was you who lost badly.

170
00:09:09,120 --> 00:09:10,760
The coach won't let a loser

171
00:09:12,000 --> 00:09:13,120
play again.

172
00:09:14,520 --> 00:09:17,360
But he has been training really hard
since his last loss.

173
00:09:17,440 --> 00:09:18,400
So what?

174
00:09:22,960 --> 00:09:24,200
It's no use talking to me.

175
00:09:25,520 --> 00:09:26,960
[Liangliang panting]

176
00:09:31,840 --> 00:09:33,720
What a brutal war.

177
00:09:34,160 --> 00:09:35,000
[Sha gasps]

178
00:09:35,160 --> 00:09:36,120
[groaning]

179
00:09:36,560 --> 00:09:37,440
Huh?

180
00:09:39,640 --> 00:09:41,040
Song Ci?

181
00:09:41,120 --> 00:09:42,560
SONG CI
XING YAO HIGH SCHOOL PLAYER

182
00:09:42,640 --> 00:09:43,680
[sighs]

183
00:09:45,440 --> 00:09:46,720
The genius player?

184
00:09:48,480 --> 00:09:49,400
[sighs]

185
00:09:49,640 --> 00:09:51,160
More like a genius sleepyhead.

186
00:09:53,800 --> 00:09:54,720
[Liangliang] Coach.

187
00:09:55,040 --> 00:09:56,200
[panting]

188
00:09:56,800 --> 00:09:57,680
Coach.

189
00:09:57,960 --> 00:09:59,120
Coach, wait.

190
00:10:02,840 --> 00:10:03,720
What's up?

191
00:10:03,960 --> 00:10:04,960
Coach.

192
00:10:06,120 --> 00:10:07,200
Please let me play.

193
00:10:08,680 --> 00:10:09,600
Coach.

194
00:10:09,960 --> 00:10:13,240
He's worked hard
ever since he lost the last game.

195
00:10:13,480 --> 00:10:14,720
His training was almost inhuman.

196
00:10:16,600 --> 00:10:17,680
[grunts]

197
00:10:18,720 --> 00:10:19,800
-[thwacks]
-[grunts]

198
00:10:21,960 --> 00:10:23,960
[somber music]

199
00:10:24,920 --> 00:10:26,760
[both grunting]

200
00:10:27,240 --> 00:10:29,880
[both breathing heavily]

201
00:10:34,160 --> 00:10:36,640
Senior, call it a day, okay?

202
00:10:37,480 --> 00:10:38,960
Mm-mm.

203
00:10:39,800 --> 00:10:40,800
No, go on.

204
00:10:42,480 --> 00:10:43,720
You push yourself too hard.

205
00:10:44,440 --> 00:10:47,080
[panting]
I said, go on.

206
00:10:48,720 --> 00:10:49,840
This kind of training

207
00:10:51,240 --> 00:10:52,560
is far from enough.

208
00:10:53,200 --> 00:10:55,520
If he cannot enter the starting lineup,

209
00:10:56,360 --> 00:10:58,600
-it's unfair.
-[scoffs]

210
00:10:59,240 --> 00:11:00,160
"Unfair"?

211
00:11:00,840 --> 00:11:01,720
Fine.

212
00:11:02,560 --> 00:11:04,440
You can also quit the starting lineup.

213
00:11:04,960 --> 00:11:06,240
-Coach.
-Coach.

214
00:11:11,040 --> 00:11:13,040
[tense music]

215
00:11:13,440 --> 00:11:15,120
[Liangliang] I will never ever
lose a game.

216
00:11:18,520 --> 00:11:20,240
[Zhiyuan] Coach, please.

217
00:11:23,160 --> 00:11:24,040
[sighs]

218
00:11:24,920 --> 00:11:27,200
I also saw how hard he was working.

219
00:11:28,720 --> 00:11:29,800
I hope...

220
00:11:33,600 --> 00:11:35,240
you can give him another chance.

221
00:11:37,320 --> 00:11:38,320
[sighs]

222
00:11:40,640 --> 00:11:41,560
Whatever.

223
00:11:45,920 --> 00:11:47,120
[gasps]

224
00:11:48,920 --> 00:11:50,840
How can you carry scissors
when practicing?

225
00:11:51,480 --> 00:11:52,480
Mind your own business.

226
00:11:52,880 --> 00:11:53,880
[camera shutter clicking]

227
00:11:54,400 --> 00:11:56,600
Captain, we will do better than our best.

228
00:12:00,080 --> 00:12:01,120
[sighs]

229
00:12:01,800 --> 00:12:04,160
Are you frightened by our cruel attitude
to our own teammates?

230
00:12:06,400 --> 00:12:08,240
We take tennis seriously.

231
00:12:09,320 --> 00:12:10,840
If you go to Yu Qing to interview,

232
00:12:11,920 --> 00:12:13,240
please help me tell Siyang

233
00:12:14,040 --> 00:12:14,960
that I will not...

234
00:12:16,120 --> 00:12:17,200
spare him this time.

235
00:12:21,040 --> 00:12:22,520
SPECIAL REPORT
ON XING YAO TENNIS CLUB

236
00:12:22,760 --> 00:12:24,240
JI JINGWU

237
00:12:24,320 --> 00:12:25,800
HUA CHONGHONG

238
00:12:29,360 --> 00:12:30,880
HU LIANGLIANG

239
00:12:31,320 --> 00:12:32,560
[sighs sharply]

240
00:12:37,200 --> 00:12:38,400
[thwacking]

241
00:12:39,960 --> 00:12:41,080
[gasping]

242
00:12:52,160 --> 00:12:53,520
[doctor] If you insist on playing,

243
00:12:54,080 --> 00:12:55,600
you should be mentally prepared for it.

244
00:12:56,200 --> 00:12:59,720
This could be your last match.

245
00:13:01,480 --> 00:13:03,480
[somber music]

246
00:13:05,840 --> 00:13:06,920
[exhales sharply]

247
00:13:14,320 --> 00:13:15,640
This is my new formula.

248
00:13:15,800 --> 00:13:17,040
I haven't tested it thoroughly.

249
00:13:20,400 --> 00:13:21,400
It's good.

250
00:13:21,840 --> 00:13:23,880
Much better than before.

251
00:13:24,520 --> 00:13:25,600
Don't worry.

252
00:13:25,880 --> 00:13:27,440
I'm improving the formula all the time.

253
00:13:31,160 --> 00:13:32,240
[soft chuckle]

254
00:13:37,680 --> 00:13:38,800
How is my new Yan-juice?

255
00:13:39,360 --> 00:13:41,320
I succeeded.
Even the captain said it's good.

256
00:13:42,080 --> 00:13:44,480
I will make adjustments on the basis
of this formula.

257
00:13:44,560 --> 00:13:45,920
Then we can start batch production.

258
00:13:46,000 --> 00:13:46,840
Mm-hm.

259
00:13:51,160 --> 00:13:52,600
Why don't you save some for me?

260
00:13:53,440 --> 00:13:54,400
I forgot.

261
00:13:55,560 --> 00:13:56,520
Are you okay?

262
00:13:57,760 --> 00:13:58,600
I'm fine.

263
00:14:02,720 --> 00:14:04,720
[comical music]

264
00:14:05,360 --> 00:14:06,360
[soft chuckle]

265
00:14:10,720 --> 00:14:11,880
It seems successful.

266
00:14:13,120 --> 00:14:14,080
[soft chuckle]

267
00:14:24,960 --> 00:14:26,360
Oh, Dachi.

268
00:14:26,880 --> 00:14:27,920
Jiale.

269
00:14:28,520 --> 00:14:31,040
Uh, why haven't you gone home?

270
00:14:31,560 --> 00:14:35,120
Oh. The teacher assigned us new homework.
I came to buy some notebooks.

271
00:14:35,440 --> 00:14:36,280
How about you?

272
00:14:36,720 --> 00:14:38,680
-Why haven't you gone home then?
-Uh...

273
00:14:39,040 --> 00:14:40,960
Oh, I ran out of pens.

274
00:14:41,080 --> 00:14:42,320
I'm here to buy some.

275
00:14:43,040 --> 00:14:44,640
-Fine.
-Hmm.

276
00:14:44,960 --> 00:14:45,800
Why do you two

277
00:14:45,880 --> 00:14:48,480
look like some middle-aged couple
who met years after their divorce?

278
00:14:48,560 --> 00:14:50,400
It's like you're acting in a movie.

279
00:14:51,640 --> 00:14:52,920
Uh...
[chuckles]

280
00:14:53,440 --> 00:14:54,480
No.

281
00:14:55,040 --> 00:14:57,000
[sighs]
That's insane.

282
00:14:57,720 --> 00:14:58,640
Oh.

283
00:14:58,720 --> 00:15:00,560
I'm going to have some omelet rice.

284
00:15:00,640 --> 00:15:02,320
You said you wanted to have some, right?

285
00:15:02,400 --> 00:15:03,960
Let's go together, okay?

286
00:15:04,080 --> 00:15:05,280
No, thanks.

287
00:15:05,360 --> 00:15:07,200
I have a lot of homework to do today.

288
00:15:07,520 --> 00:15:09,640
I have to buy the notebooks
and go back to do it.

289
00:15:09,880 --> 00:15:11,560
Oh, it's okay.

290
00:15:11,720 --> 00:15:13,320
-Go on then.
-Mm-hm.

291
00:15:18,400 --> 00:15:21,240
Ma'am, could I have an A4 ruled notebook
with horizontal lines?

292
00:15:21,320 --> 00:15:22,920
They're sold out today.

293
00:15:23,680 --> 00:15:25,680
Hey, I have one.

294
00:15:25,840 --> 00:15:27,640
Dachi, you can have it.

295
00:15:27,920 --> 00:15:28,960
Use mine first.

296
00:15:29,360 --> 00:15:31,840
How can I do that? You must need it.

297
00:15:31,920 --> 00:15:33,320
It's fine. I don't need it now.

298
00:15:34,040 --> 00:15:35,080
No, thanks.

299
00:15:35,160 --> 00:15:36,480
I can buy it somewhere else.

300
00:15:37,400 --> 00:15:38,840
Oh. Fine.

301
00:15:39,280 --> 00:15:41,040
-I'm leaving then.
-Okay.

302
00:15:42,960 --> 00:15:44,120
[sighs]

303
00:15:44,200 --> 00:15:46,000
-[chuckles]
-Are you two quarreling?

304
00:15:46,400 --> 00:15:47,440
No.

305
00:15:47,520 --> 00:15:50,240
Then why are things so awkward?
He didn't even want your exercise book.

306
00:15:50,760 --> 00:15:52,200
It's just a book.

307
00:15:52,280 --> 00:15:53,400
I've no idea what he thought.

308
00:15:53,480 --> 00:15:54,520
[chuckles]

309
00:15:57,360 --> 00:15:58,560
YU QING

310
00:15:58,640 --> 00:16:03,160
15 DAYS BEFORE YU QING VS XING YAO

311
00:16:03,760 --> 00:16:05,600
YU QING HIGH
TENNIS QUALIFYING MATCH, GROUP C

312
00:16:05,680 --> 00:16:08,760
YU QING HIGH
TENNIS QUALIFYING MATCH, GROUP D

313
00:16:11,880 --> 00:16:13,640
This is the schedule
of the qualifying match.

314
00:16:14,160 --> 00:16:15,560
Please remember your group.

315
00:16:17,160 --> 00:16:18,880
Lu Xia is in group D.

316
00:16:19,640 --> 00:16:21,640
[Xiuwen] He didn't come
to practice these days.

317
00:16:21,720 --> 00:16:23,320
Can he make it in time to the qualifying?

318
00:16:23,920 --> 00:16:25,200
Mind your own business.

319
00:16:27,760 --> 00:16:29,320
Will he come or not?

320
00:16:29,800 --> 00:16:31,520
[Xiuwen] He can't enter
the elimination match

321
00:16:32,080 --> 00:16:33,640
without playing in the qualifying match.

322
00:16:34,440 --> 00:16:35,840
How can he play against Xing Yao

323
00:16:36,920 --> 00:16:38,320
if he doesn't enter the elimination?

324
00:16:38,400 --> 00:16:39,240
[shushes]

325
00:16:41,320 --> 00:16:42,840
Maybe he is exploring a new theory.

326
00:16:43,880 --> 00:16:45,320
I wonder how it's going.

327
00:16:45,680 --> 00:16:48,920
Isn't it better if he practices with us?

328
00:16:49,000 --> 00:16:51,520
He will easily go
into a dead-end if practices alone.

329
00:16:52,520 --> 00:16:54,640
He is even more stubborn
than me sometimes.

330
00:16:55,240 --> 00:16:58,760
It's the coach's idea
to let Lu Xia practice alone.

331
00:16:58,840 --> 00:17:00,080
She has her own reason for that.

332
00:17:01,280 --> 00:17:03,280
[somber music]

333
00:17:04,359 --> 00:17:07,040
The match against Xing Yao
is crucial for us.

334
00:17:07,599 --> 00:17:10,119
[Siyang] The result determines
whether we can enter the Nationals.

335
00:17:10,480 --> 00:17:13,520
So I hope everyone
can do a good job in school qualifying.

336
00:17:14,040 --> 00:17:15,480
We will show Xing Yao...

337
00:17:16,800 --> 00:17:18,000
our strongest squad.

338
00:17:18,079 --> 00:17:20,520
-Yes.
-Yes.

339
00:17:26,880 --> 00:17:27,839
Lu Xia?

340
00:17:29,319 --> 00:17:30,280
Why are you here?

341
00:17:30,640 --> 00:17:31,640
I was always here.

342
00:17:34,640 --> 00:17:36,640
[light music]

343
00:17:39,440 --> 00:17:40,920
I have to go.

344
00:17:52,640 --> 00:17:53,640
[thwacks]

345
00:18:01,280 --> 00:18:03,840
[grunting]

346
00:18:07,160 --> 00:18:08,480
[gasps]

347
00:18:08,560 --> 00:18:11,000
[doctor] The strain of muscles and joints
will accumulate.

348
00:18:11,640 --> 00:18:15,600
So it is usually late
when you can feel the problem yourself.

349
00:18:22,520 --> 00:18:24,520
[ominous music]

350
00:18:30,440 --> 00:18:31,440
-[thwacks]
-[grunts]

351
00:18:34,200 --> 00:18:38,240
12 DAYS BEFORE YU QING VS XING YAO

352
00:18:44,280 --> 00:18:46,320
-Yan.
-Yes?

353
00:18:46,880 --> 00:18:49,080
Could I have a look
at my training plan today?

354
00:18:49,640 --> 00:18:50,720
Mm-hm.

355
00:18:51,440 --> 00:18:52,400
Oh.

356
00:18:56,160 --> 00:18:58,440
ZHUO ZHI, MU SIYANG

357
00:18:59,760 --> 00:19:01,160
Is this Siyang's training plan?

358
00:19:01,680 --> 00:19:02,520
Mm-hm.

359
00:19:02,600 --> 00:19:05,280
MU SIYANG

360
00:19:06,360 --> 00:19:07,480
Isn't it too much?

361
00:19:07,560 --> 00:19:09,400
[stutters]
Ours are all one-page training plans.

362
00:19:09,800 --> 00:19:11,120
How many pages is his?

363
00:19:12,160 --> 00:19:14,360
Siyang himself made his training plan.

364
00:19:14,440 --> 00:19:16,400
I only documented it
and made minor modifications.

365
00:19:18,640 --> 00:19:20,080
-[Baiyang snickers]
-Oh.

366
00:19:22,360 --> 00:19:24,360
[comical music]

367
00:19:24,440 --> 00:19:25,920
How long are you going to warm up for?

368
00:19:26,840 --> 00:19:28,120
We are in the same group today.

369
00:19:28,840 --> 00:19:30,160
Don't slow me down.

370
00:19:30,680 --> 00:19:31,920
It's all my fault.

371
00:19:32,680 --> 00:19:35,840
It's because of me
that Lu Xia was troubled

372
00:19:36,440 --> 00:19:37,840
and didn't show up.

373
00:19:39,120 --> 00:19:40,240
[Huang Jing] It seems like...

374
00:19:41,000 --> 00:19:42,440
I must take responsibility.

375
00:19:42,800 --> 00:19:43,760
What responsibility?

376
00:19:44,120 --> 00:19:45,240
[sighs]

377
00:19:45,360 --> 00:19:47,840
I will be Lu Xia's replacement
after he leaves.

378
00:19:49,360 --> 00:19:51,120
I will be qualified
as the winner of group C.

379
00:19:51,920 --> 00:19:52,920
You too.

380
00:19:54,080 --> 00:19:55,760
Fight when you should fight.

381
00:19:55,840 --> 00:19:56,760
[scoffs]

382
00:19:57,440 --> 00:19:58,760
[blows air]

383
00:20:01,080 --> 00:20:03,040
You haven't even
seen the group list, right?

384
00:20:03,920 --> 00:20:05,920
We are in the group of death.

385
00:20:06,680 --> 00:20:08,400
[Qiao Chen] In the same group
as the captain.

386
00:20:09,840 --> 00:20:11,680
How do you win?

387
00:20:12,120 --> 00:20:13,480
I just wish

388
00:20:13,720 --> 00:20:16,480
we won't be eliminated.

389
00:20:16,560 --> 00:20:18,560
[quirky music]

390
00:20:19,960 --> 00:20:21,560
[blowing air]

391
00:20:22,080 --> 00:20:23,800
It's okay. Just be like me.

392
00:20:24,240 --> 00:20:26,280
Focus on other games.

393
00:20:26,560 --> 00:20:27,880
Strive for those you can win.

394
00:20:28,160 --> 00:20:30,960
And just give up
when you don't see a chance.

395
00:20:32,320 --> 00:20:33,440
[sighs]

396
00:20:35,000 --> 00:20:36,000
What's on your mind?

397
00:20:38,800 --> 00:20:41,720
I'm thinking about
how to beat the captain.

398
00:20:43,960 --> 00:20:44,840
[scoffs]

399
00:20:46,880 --> 00:20:48,160
[exhales sharply]

400
00:20:50,040 --> 00:20:52,040
[comical music]

401
00:20:59,200 --> 00:21:00,240
[thwacks]

402
00:21:02,600 --> 00:21:03,640
-[thwacks]
-[Lu Xia grunts]

403
00:21:16,480 --> 00:21:17,920
[breathes heavily]

404
00:21:18,000 --> 00:21:19,760
[Lu Xia] I must find my own tennis theory.

405
00:21:20,560 --> 00:21:21,680
-[thwacks]
-[Lu Xia grunts]

406
00:21:23,560 --> 00:21:25,560
[somber music]

407
00:21:37,120 --> 00:21:39,120
[somber music continues]

408
00:21:40,800 --> 00:21:41,960
[grunts]

409
00:21:42,600 --> 00:21:43,760
The meal is ready, son.

410
00:21:43,840 --> 00:21:45,680
You've been practicing one move
for an hour.

411
00:21:48,880 --> 00:21:49,920
Let me play with you.

412
00:21:50,000 --> 00:21:51,600
I'll use only one hand, okay?

413
00:21:52,840 --> 00:21:53,880
Have your meal first.

414
00:21:54,360 --> 00:21:55,760
It's lonely to eat on my own.

415
00:21:55,840 --> 00:21:56,720
Let's play a set.

416
00:21:56,800 --> 00:21:58,480
I can also see if the grip fits properly.

417
00:21:59,040 --> 00:22:00,840
You said your hands are disabled, right?

418
00:22:02,640 --> 00:22:03,720
Bad boy.

419
00:22:04,320 --> 00:22:06,720
How can you blame your old man
when his hands got hurt?

420
00:22:07,240 --> 00:22:08,200
[Xiangqian] My goodness.

421
00:22:10,080 --> 00:22:12,080
[comical music]

422
00:22:12,520 --> 00:22:14,440
-Where are you going?
-To replace my strings.

423
00:22:15,200 --> 00:22:16,560
Let's play first.

424
00:22:18,520 --> 00:22:21,200
You can pick up the balls
if you want to do some exercise.

425
00:22:23,200 --> 00:22:24,080
Hey.

426
00:22:25,000 --> 00:22:27,000
Why is he getting angry so easily?

427
00:22:30,880 --> 00:22:31,960
[sighs]

428
00:22:32,400 --> 00:22:33,720
He cares about me.

429
00:22:34,400 --> 00:22:37,560
Son, I made you a Spanish stew.

430
00:22:49,520 --> 00:22:52,560
BAILING ISLAND

431
00:22:54,760 --> 00:22:56,360
CLOSED FOR THIS WEEKEND

432
00:22:56,440 --> 00:22:57,600
[phone beeps]

433
00:23:02,080 --> 00:23:03,400
[Qiao Chen] Where are you?

434
00:23:22,960 --> 00:23:25,360
Hello, little Lu Xia. It's been so long.

435
00:23:26,800 --> 00:23:28,800
[light music]

436
00:23:29,840 --> 00:23:31,480
It's okay that you didn't
practice with us.

437
00:23:31,560 --> 00:23:33,440
But why don't you have lunch with us?

438
00:23:34,120 --> 00:23:35,760
He's scared that you might take his food.

439
00:23:37,680 --> 00:23:38,640
You...

440
00:23:38,720 --> 00:23:39,840
We came to see you.

441
00:23:40,880 --> 00:23:43,520
We aren't in the same grade,
and you didn't come to practice.

442
00:23:43,600 --> 00:23:44,800
We can hardly meet you.

443
00:23:46,800 --> 00:23:47,680
XINGLONG

444
00:23:47,760 --> 00:23:48,720
I brought some food.

445
00:23:50,600 --> 00:23:51,800
And I brought drinks.

446
00:23:53,240 --> 00:23:54,200
[clears throat]

447
00:23:54,280 --> 00:23:57,520
Let's find a place to sit down
to have some food and drinks.

448
00:23:57,600 --> 00:23:58,480
Come on.

449
00:23:58,560 --> 00:24:00,160
[Tang Jiale chuckles]
Yes, let's go.

450
00:24:00,240 --> 00:24:01,880
-Come.
-Go.

451
00:24:07,600 --> 00:24:10,160
[Dayong] Lu Xia, when will you return?

452
00:24:10,720 --> 00:24:12,160
When I get myself ready for the game.

453
00:24:12,400 --> 00:24:13,600
How's it going?

454
00:24:16,800 --> 00:24:19,760
Um, what were you practicing on your own?

455
00:24:19,840 --> 00:24:21,800
[Tang Jiale] You are always in good form.

456
00:24:21,880 --> 00:24:23,280
You never lose.

457
00:24:23,920 --> 00:24:25,120
I keep losing.

458
00:24:27,400 --> 00:24:30,080
It's normal to lose
to a legendary player like your father.

459
00:24:30,600 --> 00:24:33,040
Do you think everyone
has no ambition like you? Loser.

460
00:24:34,000 --> 00:24:36,040
Even the most impressive people
lose sometimes.

461
00:24:36,120 --> 00:24:37,640
Even Federer loses sometimes.

462
00:24:37,720 --> 00:24:38,920
Right.

463
00:24:39,000 --> 00:24:41,560
I think it's more important
to play a match first.

464
00:24:42,280 --> 00:24:43,920
I need to be more prepared for the game.

465
00:24:44,000 --> 00:24:45,320
I can't be like this.

466
00:24:51,880 --> 00:24:53,240
Not all games can wait

467
00:24:53,840 --> 00:24:55,800
until you have reached your best form.

468
00:24:56,520 --> 00:24:58,520
[light music]

469
00:24:59,440 --> 00:25:01,440
Little Lu Xia, anyway,

470
00:25:01,520 --> 00:25:05,240
we all hope you can return
and play against Xing Yao with us.

471
00:25:06,880 --> 00:25:07,800
Hmm.

472
00:25:09,040 --> 00:25:09,920
[Zhou Zhi] Cheers.

473
00:25:14,840 --> 00:25:15,800
[Xiangqian] Come on.

474
00:25:21,520 --> 00:25:22,440
Sit.

475
00:25:25,040 --> 00:25:26,040
[groans]

476
00:25:30,760 --> 00:25:31,800
What?

477
00:25:33,320 --> 00:25:35,800
See these fishing rods here,
what else can we do?

478
00:25:39,880 --> 00:25:41,160
Are there any fish?

479
00:25:41,520 --> 00:25:43,040
Yes, I just put some in.

480
00:25:43,120 --> 00:25:45,120
[Xiangqian]
But I don't know where they are swimming.

481
00:25:45,440 --> 00:25:47,920
-I was going to cook some.
-Let's order a takeout.

482
00:25:48,000 --> 00:25:49,960
Sit, sit, sit.

483
00:25:50,960 --> 00:25:53,760
You know, many discoveries are made

484
00:25:53,840 --> 00:25:56,800
-when the giants are fishing.
-[sighing]

485
00:25:57,640 --> 00:26:00,960
You have to think like a fish
if you want to catch it.

486
00:26:01,640 --> 00:26:02,960
And you have to think

487
00:26:03,320 --> 00:26:05,440
like a master if you want to be one.

488
00:26:06,440 --> 00:26:08,440
[light music]

489
00:26:10,280 --> 00:26:11,880
If your obsession with tennis

490
00:26:12,440 --> 00:26:15,200
is only because you want
to beat different opponents,

491
00:26:15,280 --> 00:26:17,600
but you don't truly understand
who your opponents are

492
00:26:18,080 --> 00:26:21,040
and never treat them as real human beings,

493
00:26:21,840 --> 00:26:23,640
I think you should give up.

494
00:26:25,000 --> 00:26:26,560
I think I know my opponent well.

495
00:26:27,480 --> 00:26:28,600
I don't think so.

496
00:26:31,960 --> 00:26:33,920
I'm not saying you don't know me well.

497
00:26:35,520 --> 00:26:37,080
I mean, there are two on the court.

498
00:26:38,040 --> 00:26:39,880
Your real opponent is not me,

499
00:26:40,640 --> 00:26:42,080
but is the other one.

500
00:26:47,600 --> 00:26:49,320
You've been back for a long time.

501
00:26:49,680 --> 00:26:52,880
I believe you've already realized
why you choose to play tennis.

502
00:26:54,160 --> 00:26:56,920
Your opponents on the court

503
00:26:57,000 --> 00:26:59,400
come and go all the time.

504
00:27:00,200 --> 00:27:03,720
But who will always stand in your court?

505
00:27:04,800 --> 00:27:07,200
That one is your most important opponent.

506
00:27:08,120 --> 00:27:09,120
It's not me.

507
00:27:10,040 --> 00:27:11,160
I will get old.

508
00:27:14,960 --> 00:27:15,960
[Siyang] Lu Xia.

509
00:27:17,240 --> 00:27:19,240
Why do you play tennis?

510
00:27:19,680 --> 00:27:20,680
A man.

511
00:27:21,880 --> 00:27:24,880
What will you do after beating him?

512
00:27:25,480 --> 00:27:28,400
What will you gain after that?

513
00:27:28,840 --> 00:27:31,760
[Coach Muyun]
Playing tennis is like traveling.

514
00:27:32,280 --> 00:27:35,520
The journey is more important
than the destination.

515
00:27:36,560 --> 00:27:39,000
Whoever you set as your target,

516
00:27:39,480 --> 00:27:41,280
and no matter
whose skills you want to learn,

517
00:27:41,760 --> 00:27:44,240
you've only just begun to learn tennis.

518
00:27:44,560 --> 00:27:46,000
As long as you go on playing,

519
00:27:46,520 --> 00:27:48,960
you'll meet different types of players.

520
00:27:49,680 --> 00:27:50,720
[Siyang] Maybe...

521
00:27:51,360 --> 00:27:53,400
you'll meet someone stronger
than your target

522
00:27:54,600 --> 00:27:56,520
even before beating that person.

523
00:27:57,440 --> 00:27:59,600
The significance of what you're doing

524
00:28:00,360 --> 00:28:01,600
right now.

525
00:28:02,080 --> 00:28:03,280
But who

526
00:28:03,800 --> 00:28:06,040
will always stand in your court?

527
00:28:06,720 --> 00:28:09,120
That one is your most important opponent.

528
00:28:12,680 --> 00:28:13,760
Is it myself?

529
00:28:15,120 --> 00:28:16,280
[chuckles]

530
00:28:17,960 --> 00:28:19,120
I'm ordering a takeout.

531
00:28:20,760 --> 00:28:21,840
What about the fish?

532
00:28:24,080 --> 00:28:25,360
Let the fish take the bait.

533
00:28:31,320 --> 00:28:32,320
[sighs]

534
00:28:32,400 --> 00:28:35,280
[breathes deeply]

535
00:28:42,080 --> 00:28:43,560
[school bell tolling]

536
00:28:43,640 --> 00:28:45,240
7 DAYS BEFORE YU QING VS XING YAO

