00:28:45,320 --> 00:28:46,360
I was talking

538
00:28:47,040 --> 00:28:48,400
about the Enlightenment.

539
00:28:49,040 --> 00:28:51,920
[teacher] Now, let me tell you
about some thinkers

540
00:28:52,480 --> 00:28:54,200
during this period,

541
00:28:54,280 --> 00:28:56,680
as well as the significance
and differences in their ideas.

542
00:28:57,120 --> 00:28:58,880
-Now...
