687
00:36:53,240 --> 00:36:54,080
Okay.

688
00:36:55,280 --> 00:36:56,360
[sighs]

689
00:36:59,360 --> 00:37:01,360
[upbeat music]

690
00:37:08,120 --> 00:37:09,360
[grunts]

691
00:37:18,360 --> 00:37:20,640
[panting]

692
00:37:40,160 --> 00:37:42,720
Baiyang, let's be a doubles pair.

693
00:37:43,080 --> 00:37:43,920
No.

694
00:37:44,800 --> 00:37:46,400
I won't let other people affect me.

695
00:37:47,440 --> 00:37:49,120
I will win on the singles.

696
00:37:49,920 --> 00:37:52,720
